description: A package for easy integration of the AdminLTE Dashboard & Control Panel template created by Almsaeed Studio into an ASP.Net MVC web application. Includes the complete CSS, Js, and default images, plus CSHTML views, supporting C# classes for breadcrumb generation and color handling, plus an example controller and page views.

title: AdminLteMvc
